{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vasterra</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an epic journey through the mythical realm of Helheim in &quot;Vasterra.&quot; In this building and strategy game, you find yourself on a desolate island located in the underworld of Norse mythology, surrounded by the mysterious and gloomy landscape of the realm of the dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construction and Management: Build your village from scratch, improving and expanding your structures to create a thriving haven amidst the chaos of Helheim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resource Gathering: Explore the island to collect vital resources such as wood, stone, and food. Manage your supplies carefully to ensure your community's survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategic Defense: Protect your village from the fierce creatures and enemies lurking in Helheim. Strengthen your defenses, train brave warriors, and devise combat strategies to keep invaders at bay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to build, defend, and thrive in the dark and enigmatic realm of the dead? The survival of your village is in your hands!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2627720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739504148","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2627720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739504148","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2627720/27ddbcb989f516a4bd210990a13f946c5546f18c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739504148","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2627720/27ddbcb989f516a4bd210990a13f946c5546f18c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739504148","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vasterra</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\